; Miscellaneous * [[Ammar al-Baluchi]], Pakistani [[Guantanamo Bay detention camp|Guantanamo]] detainee * [[Mai Al Balushi]], Kuwaiti actress * [[Salah Abdul Rasool Al Blooshi]], Bahraini [[Guantanamo Bay detention camp|Guantanamo]] detainee
